    <string name="ai_title">AI rewrites (Gemini)</string>
    <string name="ai_instructions">To turn on \u2728 AI rewrites:\n\n1. Go to aistudio.google.com and sign in with a Google account.\n2. Open \u201CGet API key\u201D and create a free key (starts with AIza\u2026).\n3. Paste it below and tap \u201CTest &amp; save\u201D. The app asks Google which models your key can use and lists them \u2014 tap one to use.\n\nThe key and chosen model are stored only on this phone.</string>
